<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="widespread-adj">widespread <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'waɪdspred/    美 /'waɪdspred/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>广泛的；分布广的；传播广的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a widespread disease 
广泛传播的疾病</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The consequence of a rising sea level would be widespread flooding. 
海平面上升将会导致大面积的洪涝灾害。</p><footer>人教⑥ – 4</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The high cost prohibits the <strong>widespread use</strong> of the drug. 
这种药品因价格昂贵而不能广泛使用。</p></div></div>